OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FLargely dry today with very
OL,6,Fwarm sunny spells. A little cloud will
OL,7,Fbubble up in the afternoon, perhaps
OL,8,Fwith a few showers later in the
OL,9,Fafternoon. Feeling very warm in the
OL,10,Fsunshine.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA dry and warm evening with
OL,13,Flate sunshine. Skies will cloud over
OL,14,Fthrough the night with some outbreaks
OL,15,Fof rain in the early hours, turning
OL,16,Fheavy at times.
OL,17,
OL,18,CSunday:FCloudy at first in the morning
OL,19,Fwith a few showery outbreaks of rain.
OL,20,FTurning drier through the day with
OL,21,Fincreasing amounts of sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
