OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,6,FFeeling fresher in the new week.
OL,7,FLargely dry with sunny spells, but a
OL,8,Ffew showers possible at times,
OL,9,Fparticularly on Tuesday. Light winds
OL,10,Fand feeling pleasant in the sunny
OL,11,Fspells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
